            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<style>:root{color-scheme:light dark}body{font:14px/1.65 -apple-system,system-ui,sans-serif;color:#1d2122;margin:0;padding:16px 18px}h2{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 12px}ul{margin:0;padding-left:18px}li{margin:6px 0}li::marker{color:#f9a600}@media (prefers-color-scheme:dark){body{color:#e7e9ea}}</style>
<h2>What’s new in 0.2.0</h2><ul>
<li>Builds, saves, and publishing now show clear errors instead of failing silently</li>
<li>Large projects save in the background without freezing the canvas</li>
<li>More reliable publishing to Vercel, with automatic retries on network hiccups</li>
<li>The live preview recovers from start-up problems instead of showing a blank page</li>
<li>New Settings window: use your own Pexels API key and manage anonymous usage sharing</li>
<li>Stability and performance improvements across the editor</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
